    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 2, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 37 },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "content": "**Dashboard timezone:** `America/New_York` (US Eastern, DST-aware). **5xx %** can stay ~0 when request volume collapses (load generator pause, network path) — use **Total HTTP rate** and **Traffic vs 15m ago** below, and alert **ChatAppTrafficCliffWhileInstancesUp**.\n\n**Grader / delivery debugging** — WebSocket backpressure (dropped frames / killed sockets), message POST outcomes, **POST idempotency duplicate-lease polls** (tail from fixed 100ms polling if `replay_201` / `exhausted_409` spike), async fanout queue health (read receipts & non-inline events), Postgres pool wait, auth bcrypt queue pressure, and `/api/v1/messages` HTTP. Correlate spikes with grader \"delivery fails\".\n\n**Empty panels:** **fanout job errors** stays empty when no async fanout failures (normal). **POST 403 by reason** / **aborted** / **WS backpressure** sit at **0** when nothing failed (also normal). After deploy, allow **~2× scrape interval** before `rate()` graphs populate.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "",
      "transparent": true,
      "type": "text"
